General.Name: Galena Mining Ltd
General.Description: Galena Mining Limited engages in the acquisition and exploration of mineral projects in Australia. The company operates through Abra Mine, Exploration, and Other Activities segments. It explores for copper, gold, lead, silver, zinc, and manganese deposits. The company owns 60% interest in the Abra Base Metals lead-silver project located in the Gascoyne region, Western Australia. It holds 100% interest in Jillawarra prospects. Galena Mining Limited was incorporated in 2016 and is based in West Perth, Australia.
